  "title": "Sales Manager (Generator)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive sales of generator rental and purchase packages</li>\n  <li>Manage and grow client relationships</li>\n  <li>Respond to enquiries and prepare quotations</li>\n  <li>Develop new business opportunities in Singapore &amp; SEA</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with technical and operations teams</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience in B2B sales (equipment/power industry preferred)</li>\n  <li>Strong communication and negotiation skills</li>\n  <li>Independent and target-driven</li>\n  <li>Willing to travel regionally</li>\n  <li>Possess Class 3 license (advantageous)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>",
